name: Madosi Wewedi
description: "Madosi Wewedi" are javanese words. "Madosi" means searching while "wewedi" is satan. Babywatan is growing up. he is searching what life could give. what is black and what is white. Life is great, drunk, drugs, sex. too high to step on earth. Babywatan is dwelling while the demon is watching. life is great my friend.
